title: Business Formations Within 4 Quarters for District of Columbia (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFBF4QTOTALNSADC (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFBF4QTOTALNSADC) for an alternative.

This series provides the number of employer businesses that originate from Business Applications (BA) within four quarters from the quarter of application. By definition, the end-point of this series is determined by the most recent quarter for which the administrative data is available on payroll.
